{"tid":332400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掛八號先敢唔返工奴性盡顯","createTime":"2017-07-23T03:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T03:54:10.000Z","uid":66686,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07cbebd44853b7c25cc15e64ac5b62955cfd31d5","tid":332400,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"係度屌一至五唔掛八號只掛三號，老實講如果有危險可以唔返，打俾老闆講返聲最多未扣返年假或無薪假。都唔明有乜好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb4a90f42cab3b2f75fe2a66037842c1c9dec18","tid":332400,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"因為你份工人工低職位低，無滿足感難怪你咁諗！"},{"pid":"663e5ce45925616221d14452ccc69e3670f0c5ce","tid":332400,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"通常做最低層既人返工覺得係交差係受罪<br />\n<br />\n做得高級先會明白返工係管人係有滿足感，並唔係你所講既奴性！"}]}